---
<section id="how-it-works" data-test="how-it-works-section" class="py-20 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4 text-[var(--fg)]">Four skills. One methodology.</h2>
    <p class="text-center text-[var(--muted)] mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      RootSpec breaks the spec-to-ship pipeline into four composable skills you can run at any stage of development.
    </p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-800 bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-950/30">
        <div class="font-mono text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 font-bold text-lg mb-2">rs-init</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-[var(--fg)]">Initialize</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--muted)]">Scaffold the spec directory, conventions, and test infrastructure for your project.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-950/30">
        <div class="font-mono text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold text-lg mb-2">rs-spec</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-[var(--fg)]">Specify</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--muted)]">Transform a product seed into a structured 5-level specification with user stories and acceptance criteria.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-cyan-200 dark:border-cyan-800 bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-950/30">
        <div class="font-mono text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg mb-2">rs-impl</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-[var(--fg)]">Implement</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--muted)]">Build features from user stories, test-driven, one story at a time, with automated verification.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-green-200 dark:border-green-800 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-950/30">
        <div class="font-mono text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 font-bold text-lg mb-2">rs-validate</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-[var(--fg)]">Validate</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--muted)]">Run a full review pass — automated tests, spec coverage, and LLM review — to surface gaps.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
